<1.0.0>
### ✨ New Features
- Added **Feather-Menu notifications** for smoother UI feedback.
- Integrated **BccUtils RPC** for cleaner and more reliable client–server communication.
- Added the ability to **mark messages as unread**.
- Added an automatic check every **15 minutes** to notify players if they have unread messages.
- Players can now **buy letters directly from mailbox locations**.
- Introduced **durability for letters** to simulate wear and tear.
- Added several new **API endpoints** for developers.

### 🧰 Fixes & Improvements
- Fixed issue where mailboxes were only registered at specific locations.
- Fixed multiple **menu-related issues**.
- Removed unnecessary **string formatting in menus**.
- Various other **stability and performance improvements**.
